# =====================================================
# AGENT:
# Doel: Repository schoon en reproduceerbaar houden op dev machines en CI.
# Bereik: U mag ignore-patronen toevoegen/verwijderen; negeer geen source, docs of configs die versiebeheerd moeten worden.
# Niet: Voeg geen tool-specifieke regels toe tenzij gerechtvaardigd door repo-inhoud.
# Regels:
#   - Voorkeuren voor algemene patronen boven machine-specifieke paden.
#   - Nooit negeren: /docs, /src, /db/migrations (indien aanwezig)
#   - Wel negeren: geheimen en lokale env-bestanden.
# Uitvoer: Een leesbare, gegroepeerde .gitignore met korte sectiekoppen.
# =====================================================
# ===================================
# Werkruimte Mappen (Runtime/Cache)
# ===================================
# Agent cache en synchronisatie
mandarin-agents/
mandarin-canon/

concepts/

# Logs van fetch-bewerkingen en agent runs
logs/

# Lokale instellingen (niet delen)
settings.json

# Tijdelijke bestanden en werkruimten
temp/

# Agent prompt-instructies (lokale runtime)
prompt-instructions/*.md
!prompt-instructions/README.md

# Canon map (experimenteel/concept)
canon/

# ===================================
# Python
# ===================================
# Byte-compiled / optimized / DLL bestanden
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# Virtuele omgevingen
venv/
env/
ENV/
.venv/

# Distributie / packaging
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/

# ===================================
# Editor / IDE
# ===================================
# VS Code werkruimte bestanden (maar behoud instellingen/taken)
*.code-workspace

# JetBrains (PyCharm, IntelliJ, etc.)
.idea/
*.iml

# Sublime Text
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

# Vim
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Emacs
*~
\#*\#
.\#*

# ===================================
# Besturingssysteem Bestanden
# ===================================
# macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
._*

# Windows
Thumbs.db
Thumbs.db:encryptable
ehthumbs.db
ehthumbs_vista.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# Linux
.directory
.Trash-*

# ===================================
# Git
# ===================================
*.orig
*.rej
*.patch

# ===================================
# Diversen
# ===================================
# Test artefacten
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/

# Backup bestanden
*.bak
*.backup
*~

# Lock bestanden (optioneel - uitschakelen indien gewenst)
# poetry.lock
# Pipfile.lock
# =====================================================
# AGENT:
# Purpose: Keep repository clean and reproducible across dev machines and CI.
# Scope: You may add/remove ignore patterns; do not ignore source, docs, or configs that must be versioned.
# Non-Goals: Do not add tool-specific rules unless justified by repo content.
# Rules:
#   - Prefer general patterns over machine-specific paths.
#   - Never ignore: /docs, /src, /db/migrations (if present)
#   - Do ignore secrets and local env files.
# Output: A readable, grouped .gitignore with short section headers.
# =====================================================
# ===================================
# Workspace Folders (Runtime/Cache)
# ===================================
# Agent cache en synchronisatie
mandarin-agents/

concepts/

# Logs van fetch operaties en agent runs
logs/

# own settings (lokale configuratie, niet delen)
settings.json


# Tijdelijke bestanden en workspaces
temp/

# Agent prompt-instructies (lokale runtime)
prompt-instructions/*.md
!prompt-instructions/README.md

# Canon folder (experimenteel/draft)
canon/

# ===================================
# Python
# ===================================
# Byte-compiled / optimized / DLL files
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

